dude , first off try to unzip one of the files with winrar, ya only need to do one and it'll put it all together from there. then ya should end up with a .bin and a .cue file. download daemon tools and install that. daemon tools is a program that lets ya mount images of a cd instead of actually burning it. set the number of drives on daemon tools to at least 1 , and mount the .cue file with that . it'll show up as you having that cd in a drive .after that ya should be able to figure it out yourself.

För att mounta: Högerklcika på Deamon Tools icon nere i vertygsfältet --> Sen Virtual CD/DVD-rom --> Sen sätter du markeringen övber device 1,2,3... och trycker på Mount Image och sen väljer du den filen du vill mounta... Svårare än så är de tinte :D
